Market News April 4, 2018 / 1:21 PM / in 9 minutes BRIEF-Siemens Canada Secures Order From Inter Pipeline To Supply 2 Industrial Gas Turbines For Cogeneration Project In Alberta Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 4 (Reuters) - Siemens AG: 
* RECEIVED AN ORDER FROM INTER PIPELINE TO SUPPLY 2 INDUSTRIAL GAS TURBINES FOR COGENERATION PROJECT IN ALBERTA, CANADA Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
